criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Major patient;

          -  Patient affiliated to a social security scheme;

          -  Patient suffering from Chronic Myeloid Leukemia, taking a Tyrosine Kinase Inhibitor
             (Imatinib, Nilotinib, Dasatinib, or Bosutinib);

          -  Molecular response < 4,5 Log;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Legal incapacity or limited capacity ; Medical or psychological incapacity or limited
             capacity;

          -  Not able to read and/or to write French;

          -  Patient taking Ponatinib.
